stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> draft: Finance 生成发票
    draft --> pending_review: 需要内部审核
    draft --> sent: Finance 发送给客户
    pending_review --> sent: 审核通过后发送
    sent --> paid: 客户全额付款
    sent --> partially_paid: 客户部分付款
    sent --> overdue: Job 5 自动标记\n(超过 Due Date)
    partially_paid --> paid: 补齐尾款
    overdue --> paid: 客户付款
    draft --> cancelled: 作废
    sent --> void: 发票冲销

    classDef auto fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:2px
    classDef finance fill:#F3E5F5,stroke:#9C27B0,stroke-width:2px
    classDef terminal fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#F44336,stroke-width:2px
    classDef success fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:2px

    class draft,pending_review finance
    class sent finance
    class overdue auto
    class paid,partially_paid success
    class cancelled,void terminal
